tweet: Finally, it reauthorizes the Rural Energy Savings Program, which is already helping South Carolinians and families in rural communities across the country save $$$ on utility costs by investing in energy efficiency.  I am proud to support it on the floor today. (3/3) #Farmbill
The bill will also expand broadband access in rural communities which is key to ensuring no community is left behind in the modern era. (2/3) #FarmBill

The Farm Bill preserves the safety net to ensure families & children in need won't go hungry, rolling back Republican efforts to destroy nutrition aid.  As Matthew 25 teaches us, “whatever you did for one of the least of these brothers and sisters of mine, you did for me” (1/3)
